{"tid":2047914,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"獨家: 拼多多回港上市，中金為保薦人","createTime":"2020-06-02T12:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T16:32:43.000Z","uid":1086,"like":7,"dislike":124,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"1c72fcc474e34a2ba3b5b673050cd2d7915ab4c1","tid":2047914,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:24:56.000Z","msg":"騰訊新聞《一線》獨家獲悉，拼多多確定回港二次上市，並​​確定了中金為其保薦人之一。據知情人士透露，拼多多上市團隊原計劃6月中旬交表，但是不排除提速。具體的交表時間暫未獲悉。<br />\n<br />\n拼多多能夠&ldquo;提速&rdquo;是因為港交所上市委員會全力推近中概股回港二次上市，為所有的中概股在港上市提速&ldquo;開綠燈&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n拼多多也是至今&ldquo;最年輕&rdquo;回港二次上市的中概股。 2018年7月27日，成立僅34個月的拼多多赴美上市，其當時的承銷團為高盛和中金。<br />\n<br />\n拼多多於5月22日發布了今年第一度財報，其營收65.41億元，同比增長44%，淨虧損31.70億元，相較於去年同期淨虧損13.79億元有擴大。<br />\n<br />\n不過，拼多多在第一季度保持了40%以上的用戶增速，其中平均月活用戶數達到4.87億，較2019年同期增長1.98億。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n目前拼多多市值約6104億港元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78afb0e3f772fda3b419e57d78cc92d5be8f340f","tid":2047914,"uid":91813,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:26:22.000Z","msg":"唔怪得要升咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007a3fafa0dd153628bce9eea231cf93815fabaf","tid":2047914,"uid":129895,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"拼多多好似專賣老翻<br />\n咁都可以上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1111d067e79e467d8d20942527d56e2dd4a293c1","tid":2047914,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://new.qq.com/omn/20200601/20200601A0LQD400.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Fomn%2F20200601%2F20200601A0LQD400.html&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=cfee1466\" target=\"_blank\">https://new.qq.com/omn/20200601/20200601A0LQD400.html</a>"},{"pid":"f422e00295d005bac3aafc961d925ece50db0518","tid":2047914,"uid":3302,"like":28,"dislike":2,"sc