tid":2047914,"uid":36132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:25:06.000Z","msg":"拼多多回應&ldquo;二次上市&rdquo;：公司現金儲備充裕， 暫無任何計劃<br />\n6月2日晚間，有媒體發佈&ldquo;獨家消息&rdquo;稱，拼多多將確定回港二次上市，並表示確定中金為其保薦人之一。報道援引知情人士的説法稱，拼多多上市團隊原計劃6月中旬交表，但不排除提速。對此，拼多多(PDD.O)發言人迴應稱，&ldquo;我們從未與任何中介機構探討過這一計劃，也未與任何交易所有過任何關於&lsquo;二次上市&rsquo;話題的接觸，不知這樣的獨家消息從何而來。&rdquo;發言人還稱，公司現金流健康，截至目前的資金儲備和收入增速足以讓&ldquo;百億補貼&rdquo;持續多年，所以暫無任何二次上市計劃。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca53182e9fbd6ca593541e6aeb9474f542ab25c9","tid":2047914,"uid":27530,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f16256732688ef6cda6c4892c453b9a938501d6","tid":2047914,"uid":61840,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"1111d067e79e467d8d20942527d56e2dd4a293c1","tid":2047914,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:29:22.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<a href=\"https://new.qq.com/omn/20200601/20200601A0LQD400.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnew.qq.com%2Fomn%2F20200601%2F20200601A0LQD400.html&d=Lcx8qPwugtyypLbLLwesbWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=cfee1466\" target=\"_blank\">https://new.qq.com/omn/20200601/20200601A0LQD400.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T12:30:26.000Z","msg":"屌你老母send條大陸link出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:31:39.000Z","msg":"收皮啦，唔send link點比source呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b831a14c233cdc1141163a8aad1a765f15a47cfa","tid":2047914,"uid":31835,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T13:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDn9S0D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDn9S0D.jpg&h=7f59614f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b783d67bbf615afd57df